title: Canelo Alvarez KOs Caleb Plant With Crazy Uppercut | SHOWTIME PPV
author: SHOWTIME Sports
description:
Boxing’s biggest star, four-division world champion Canelo Álvarez knocked out Caleb Plant with a crazy uppercut in round 11 to become the 6th undisputed male champion in boxing history.
